<div class="container-custom py-8">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: <%= Date.current.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden mb-6">
      <div class="p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">What Are Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Cookies are small text files that are placed on your computer or mobile device when you visit our website.
          They are widely used to make websites work more efficiently and provide a better user experience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden mb-6">
      <div class="p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">How We Use Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">BioGrammatics uses cookies to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-700">
          <li>Keep you signed in to your account</li>
          <li>Remember your preferences and settings</li>
          <li>Understand how you use our website (with your consent)</li>
          <li>Improve our services based on usage patterns</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden mb-6">
      <div class="p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-4">Types of Cookies We Use</h2>

        <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mt-4 mb-2">
          Essential Cookies <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-blue-600 text-white ml-2">Always Active</span>
        </h5>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly. They enable core functionality such as:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li><strong>session_id:</strong> Maintains your login session</li>
          <li><strong>cookie_consent:</strong> Remembers your cookie preferences</li>
          <li><strong>csrf_token:</strong> Security token to prevent cross-site request forgery</li>
        </ul>

        <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mt-4 mb-2">
          Analytics Cookies <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-gray-500 text-white ml-2">Optional</span>
        </h5>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">When enabled, these cookies help us understand how visitors interact with our website:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li><strong>Google Analytics (_ga, _gid):</strong> Tracks page views and user behavior (if implemented)</li>
          <li>All data is anonymized and aggregated</li>
        </ul>

        <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mt-4 mb-2">
          Marketing Cookies <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-gray-500 text-white ml-2">Optional</span>
        </h5>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">When enabled, these cookies may be used to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-700">
          <li>Show relevant advertisements on other websites</li>
          <li>Measure the effectiveness of our marketing campaigns</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden mb-6">
      <div class="p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">Your Cookie Choices</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li><strong>Accept or Reject:</strong> Choose which types of cookies you want to accept</li>
          <li><strong>Change Preferences:</strong> Update your cookie settings at any time via the "Cookie Settings" link in the footer</li>
          <li><strong>Browser Settings:</strong> Control cookies through your browser settings</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
          <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle text-yellow-600 text-xl flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
          <div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              <strong class="text-charcoal">Note:</strong> Disabling essential cookies may prevent you from using certain features of our website,
              such as signing in to your account or making purchases.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden mb-6">
      <div class="p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">Third-Party Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
          We may use services from third parties that set their own cookies. These are governed by the privacy policies
          of those third parties:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Bootstrap CDN:</strong> For loading CSS and JavaScript frameworks</li>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> For website analytics (only with your consent)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden mb-6">
      <div class="p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">How to Control Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">You can control cookies through:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li><strong>Our Cookie Settings:</strong> Click "Cookie Settings" in the footer</li>
          <li><strong>Browser Settings:</strong> Most browsers allow you to refuse or delete cookies</li>
          <li><strong>Private Browsing:</strong> Use incognito or private browsing mode</li>
        </ul>

        <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mt-4 mb-2">Browser-Specific Instructions:</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-700">
          <li><a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-bio-green hover:text-bio-green-dark font-medium">Chrome</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/cookies-information-websites-store-on-your-computer" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-bio-green hover:text-bio-green-dark font-medium">Firefox</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-and-website-data-sfri11471/mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-bio-green hover:text-bio-green-dark font-medium">Safari</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/17442/windows-internet-explorer-delete-manage-cookies" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-bio-green hover:text-bio-green-dark font-medium">Internet Explorer/Edge</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden mb-6">
      <div class="p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by updating the
          "Last updated" date at the top of this policy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden mb-6">
      <div class="p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">If you have questions about our use of cookies, please contact us at:</p>
        <address class="text-gray-700 not-italic">
          <strong class="text-charcoal">BioGrammatics</strong><br>
          Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@biogrammatics.com" class="text-bio-green hover:text-bio-green-dark font-medium">privacy@biogrammatics.com</a><br>
          <%= link_to "Privacy Policy", privacy_path, class: "text-bio-green hover:text-bio-green-dark font-medium" %><br>
        </address>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <button type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors" onclick="manageCookies()">
        <i class="bi bi-gear mr-2"></i>Manage Cookie Settings
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
